Wrasslin' Cage Match

2933163 ⋅ DB ⋅ EXU

✅ ❌ 🪓 💼 🗑️
effect

  • When this card is activated: You can Special Summon 1 "Wrasslin' Gatr" from your hand, Deck or GY, but you cannot Summon monsters while that monster is face-up on the field, except "Wrasslin" monsters. If a "Wrasslin'" monster(s) you control that is neither a Fusion Monster nor a Ritual Monster is destroyed by battle: You can Special Summon 1 "Wrasslin' Jaguar" from your Extra Deck or 1 "Wrasslin' Eagle" from your Deck, ignoring its Summoning conditions. During your Main Phase: You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls and 1 "Wrasslin'" monster you control; your opponent's monster's ATK/DEF become the same as your monster's ATK/DEF. You can only use each effect of "Wrasslin' Cage Match" once per turn.

➡️

You can only use 1 effect of "Wrasslin' Tag Team" per turn, and only once that turn.

effect

You can only use 1 “Draclash Samurai” effect per turn, and only once that turn.
